{"tid":113042,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"初出黎做嘢既煩惱","createTime":"2017-02-08T15:30:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T08:03:47.000Z","uid":5857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ccb9e7744a8a086af73da3b2a5cebd939e096561","tid":113042,"uid":5857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:30:38.000Z","msg":"小弟初出黎做嘢<br />\n有時收左工 or 返完夜校 <br />\n之後個人完全唔想理人，返到屋企，屋企人問你野/關心你，都會覺得佢地好撚煩<br />\n佢地係隔離嗶哩扒啦嗶哩扒啦<br />\n之後我就爆計話咪撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實係咪正常？<br />\n定係我EQ太低<br />\n有冇咩巴絲打可以俾下意見點改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知道屋企人係為我好但係個刻真係好燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d335801ce037381b38765bea5ef95c618e5316d","tid":113042,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:33:57.000Z","msg":"出來做野係咁，慢慢你就習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以放到工已經好好ga la"},{"pid":"56fffa687982c65f4763a88b0ce8dc2df59990ce","tid":113042,"uid":5857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:42:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出來做野係咁，慢慢你就習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以放到工已經好好ga la</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能係我入世未深<br />\n事後回想係覺得好對唔住屋企人<br />\n但係又好難開口say sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd1fa9a2fdc7e0d55240b34e0e4df9e1a879775","tid":113042,"uid":4790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:43:01.000Z","msg":"我都係 放工就想返屋企 放假就想係屋企休息 完全唔想出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26231b0e505799b7fdea54e69298493d0c272d51","tid":113042,"uid":82346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:43:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出來做野係咁，慢慢你就習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以放到工已經好好ga la</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能係我入世未深<br />\n事後回想係覺得好對唔住屋企人<br />\n但係又好難開口say sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一定要講出黎<br />\n<br />\n唔係後悔...你一認錯..兩老就好開心<br />\n<br />\n其實佢地可能介意"},{"pid":"e0c9ae50f3b3dcc4f4c02edc35a0acb27206ae54","tid":113042,"uid":5857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:49:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係 放工就想返屋企 放假就想係屋企休息 完全唔想出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同感<br />\n之後個人就變得越黎越毒<br />\n朋友因爲少聯絡而少左"},{"pid":"c5782de447a9b7a46aadc97f96ff6289f00fa21e","tid":113042,"uid":5857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:50:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>出來做野係咁，慢慢你就習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以放到工已經好好ga la</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能係我入世未深<br />\n事後回想係覺得好對唔住屋企人<br />\n但係又好難開口say sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一定要講出黎<br />\n<br />\n唔係後悔...你一認錯..兩老就好開心<br />\n<br />\n其實佢地可能介意</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次會試下道歉<br />\n真係有啲難開口"},{"pid":"2c793234e1ac88aa9fc965cd7d4763f228f40016","tid":113042,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:51:14.000Z","msg":"打工仔心情差好正常，我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9708039bf06b34f6ccdef79188c07926cb1d5ffe","tid":113042,"uid":76747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:52:41.000Z","msg":"正常, 所以有時搭車番放工/渣車<br />\n果段時間先係真正屬於自己"},{"pid":"4570bb128d188dac53e57860608f264c7a84ecaf","tid":113042,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s